Ön Genius kedvezményre jogosult Casa Azul - Linda casa Familiar com Piscina no Peró em Cabo Frio szálláshelyén! Hogy spórolhasson ezen a szálláson, csupán be kell lépnie.

Featuring air-conditioned accommodation with a private pool, Casa Azul - Linda casa Familiar com Piscina no Peró em Cabo Frio is located in Cabo Frio. Popular points of interest nearby include Municipal Theater, Water Square and Municipal Estadium Alair Correia. Foguete Beach is 2.8 km from the holiday home and Japanese Island is 8.9 km away. The spacious holiday home is equipped with 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a dining area, a fully equipped kitchen, and a balcony with pool views. For added privacy, the accommodation has a private entrance and is protected by full-day security. Guests at the holiday home will be able to enjoy activities in and around Cabo Frio, like walking tours. Popular points of interest near Casa Azul - Linda casa Familiar com Piscina no Peró em Cabo Frio include Praia do Forte, Dunes Park and Surf Museum. The nearest airport is Cabo Frio International Airport, 5 km from the accommodation.
